        Django TileStache
        =============================
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-tilestache.svg
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-tilestache
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/george-silva/django-tilestache.svg?branch=master
